{"pageProps":{"data":{"news_id":"605","news_catgory":"1","hot_news":"0","news_push":"","news_on_top":"1","news_title":"雪梨一天燒掉5,000萬美元 澳洲野火肆虐經濟損失慘重","news_summary":"","image_path":"","news_des":null,"news_content":"<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span lang='EN-US' style='mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;&#10;font-family:'>2020-01-03 02:02 </span><span style='mso-bidi-font-size:&#10;12.0pt;font-family:'>經濟日報 編譯易起宇／綜合外電</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span lang='EN-US' style='mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;&#10;font-family:'>&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span lang='EN-US' style='mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;&#10;font-family:'><img alt='' src='/user_files/news_files/%E6%BE%B3%E6%B4%B2%E9%87%8E%E7%81%AB(1).jpg' style='width: 800px; height: 533px;' /></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span style='mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:'>澳洲野火造成驚人經損，濃煙也嚴重影響當地居民的健康。 美聯社</span></span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<hr />\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:'>雖然森林野火是澳洲每年都會遭遇的問題，但今年的規模卻是前所未見。死亡人數日益攀升、數百萬公頃土地被燒燬 、大量房屋被燒成廢墟。分析師表示，今年澳洲野火所造成的經濟損失，光是雪梨每天就可能超過<span lang='EN-US'>5,000</span>萬美元。</span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:'>英國每日電訊報報導，截自<span lang='EN-US'>2</span>日為止，澳洲已有約<span lang='EN-US'>550</span>萬公頃（<span lang='EN-US'>1,350</span>萬英畝）土地被燒燬，比丹麥或荷蘭的面積還大，光是新南威爾斯省被燒毀的土地面積就有約<span lang='EN-US'>1,000</span>萬英畝。新南威爾斯省消防局表示，過去幾年該省遭到野火燒毀的面積只有<span lang='EN-US'>28</span>萬公頃。去年亞馬遜雨林遭燒毀的面積只有約<span lang='EN-US'>90</span>萬公頃。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:'>遭到野火祝融的房屋數量已逾<span lang='EN-US'>1,300</span>棟，確認死亡人數已攀至<span lang='EN-US'>18</span>人。但因為有些地區至今仍火勢猛烈，消防員難以進入救援，這些數字預料都將繼續升高。有些城鎮甚至已因為這場大火幾乎在地圖上消失。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:'>SGS Economics &amp; Planning</span><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:'>分析師表示，今年澳洲野火所造成的經濟損失，光是雪梨每天就可能超過<span lang='EN-US'>5,000</span>萬美元。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:'>這還不包含大火濃煙對當地居民健康造成的傷害，這將會對澳洲政府的財政支出造成巨大衝擊。雪梨目前已是全球空氣品質最糟的城市之一。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:'>澳洲當局表示，大火濃煙已覆蓋包括雪梨、坎培拉等城市，製造出的汙染物濃度是對人體有害等級濃度的<span lang='EN-US'>11</span>倍。雪梨的空氣品質已有至少<span lang='EN-US'>30</span>天處於危險等級。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:'>在去年<span lang='EN-US'>10</span>月到<span lang='EN-US'>12</span>月底間，澳洲申請保險理賠的總金額為<span lang='EN-US'>2.4</span>億美元，其中約有<span lang='EN-US'>2,306</span>件、價值約<span lang='EN-US'>1.83</span>億美元的申請案件，都是因為新南威爾斯省中北部海岸和昆士蘭省的野火。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:'>德勤（<span lang='EN-US'>Deloitte</span>）<span lang='EN-US'>2017</span>年表示，澳洲天然災害所造成的損失愈來愈多，在<span lang='EN-US'>2050</span>年前每年損失將達到<span lang='EN-US'>390</span>億美元。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span style='mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:'>資料來源<span lang='EN-US'>: https://udn.com/news/story/6811/4264562?from=udn-relatednews_ch2</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n","keyword":"","news_order_id":"0","create_date":"2020-01-06","clk_count":"140"}},"__N_SSG":true}